{"tid":2087502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明前最黑暗","createTime":"2020-06-30T16:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T17:14:02.000Z","uid":210839,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"de6448dcf57992f22658450395c9bc7fbbfbb1bc","tid":2087502,"uid":210839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:51:57.000Z","msg":"可惜黑暗係無盡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHK 1997-2020<br />\n<br />\nRIP"},{"pid":"223507ade855acee735054e8c193542bfb79779c","tid":2087502,"uid":266503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:53:02.000Z","msg":"「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"ddcf450613a0195f119dd60b0dd88326d7258376","tid":2087502,"uid":106929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:53:08.000Z","msg":"唔知會唔會有重光既一日<br />\n<br />\n有生之年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a76349ba5deb72dc0e6eb95176ba3b2626a51d1","tid":20